</span> is the <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Refractive_index" title="Refractive index" id="mwuA">refractive index</a> of the lens material,</dd>
<dd id="mwuQ"><span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt212" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"R_1"}}' id="mwug"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle R_{1}}">
