<p id="mw-w">This can also be put into the "Newtonian" form:</p>

<dl id="mw_A"><dd id="mw_Q"><span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt226" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"x_1 x_2 = f^2,\\!"}}' id="mw_g"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle x_{1}x_{2}=f^{2},\!}">
