AyI">Bibcode</a>:<a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2008Natur.455..376V" id="mwAyM">2008Natur.455..376V</a>. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier" id="mwAyQ">doi</a>:<a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="//doi.org/10.1038%2Fnature07247" id="mwAyU">10.1038/nature07247</a>. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./PubMed_Identifier" title="PubMed Identifier" id="mwAyY" class="mw-redirect">PMID</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwAyc"> </span><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/18690249" id="mwAyg">18690249</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Nature&amp;rft.atitle=Three-dimensional+optical+metamaterial+with+a+negative+refractive+index&amp;rft.volume=455&amp;rft.issue=7211&amp;rft.pages=376-9&amp;rft.date=2008&amp;rft_id=info%3Apmid%2F18690249&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1038%2Fnature07247&amp;rft_id=info%3Abibcode%2F2008Natur.455..376V&amp;rft.aulast=Valentine&amp;rft.aufirst=J.&amp;rft.au=Zhang%2C+Shuang&amp;rft.au=Zentgraf%2C+Thomas&amp;rft.au=Ulin-Avila%2C+Erick&amp;rft.au=Genov%2C+Dentcho+A.&amp;rft.au=Bartal%2C+Guy&amp;rft.au=Zhang%2C+Xiang&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALens+%28optics%29" class="Z3988" about="#mwt123" id="mwAyk"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt123" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwAyo"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-30" id="cite_note-30"><a href="./Lens_(optics)#cite_ref-30" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-30" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation journal" about="#mwt124" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt